1. git clone https://github.com/adaman79/vagrant_opencms.git
2. vagrant up opencms
3. sudo service mysql restart
4. Open your web browser and go to http://THE_BRIDGED_IP_OF_THE_VAGRANT_BOX:8080/opencms/setup/
5. Run setup {Setup Connection: user => root with pwd => toor and OpenCms Connection with user => opencms and pwd => opencms} have fun.
